
 TrinteJS MVC Bootstrapper
 This is the default usage help.

 Usage: trinte [options]

 Options:

  -h, --help       output usage information
  -V, --version    output the version number
  -f, --force      force on non-empty directory
  -i, --init       create new mvc project
  
  --sessions       add session support
  --jade           add view engine support (ejs|jade|jshtml|haml|hogan) 
                   defaults to ejs.
  --auth           add authorization support (dependency to everyauth)
  --coffee         add coffee script support (defaults to js)
  --less           add stylesheet support (css|less|stylus|sass) 
                   defaults to plain css.
  --force          force on non-empty directory
  
 Create Application example:
  
   $ trinte init myapp --sessions --auth --jade --coffee

    create : myapp
    create : myapp/package.json
    create : myapp/app.js
    create : myapp/app-cluster.js
    create : myapp/public
    create : myapp/public/js
    create : myapp/public/img
    create : myapp/public/css
    create : myapp/public/css/...
    create : myapp/config
    create : myapp/config/...
    create : myapp/app
    create : myapp/app/controllers
   ...

 Install dependencies:
   $ cd myapp && npm install
  
 Run the app:
   $ trinte  